<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\user_com_interface\elasock\sam02">gethostname</sample>
    <volume>elasock API</volume>
    <title>gethostname</title>
    <routine_idx>ElastosSocketIndex.htm</routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>返回本地主机的标准主机名。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>char*</param_type>
                <param_name>name</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[out]存放主机名的缓冲区。</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>namelen</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]缓冲区长度。</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>如果成功，gethostname返回0。否则，返回SOCKET_ERROR，应用程序可通过<link url="WSAGetLastError.htm">WSAGetLastError()</link>获取相应错误代码。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>暂不支持。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <system>
            <system_name>
                Elastos 操作系统
            </system_name>
        </system>
        <headerfile>
            <file_name> winsock.h</file_name>
        </headerfile>
        <library>
            <lib_name> ElSocket.lib  </lib_name>
        </library>
    </requirements>

    <references>
